Live at the Wiltern is an album by English indie rock band Florence and the Machine. It consists of a recording of a concert at the Wiltern Theatre in Los Angeles, which took place on 7 November 2010. It was released exclusively to the iTunes Store. It was also accompanied by a film version of the concert.
